    "description": "<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094550/extras/95d3829d5a7937830e1ba36a2704118f.avif?t=1707744718\" width=640 height=100 /></span> 。<br><br>Saga of Sins是一个邪恶的动作冒险游戏，具有神秘的故事情节和奖励性的街机游戏玩法! 沉浸在一个由荷兰画家Hieronymus Bosch（1450-1516）启发的彩色玻璃世界中，这个世界被罪恶所玷污。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094550/extras/e249eb049dfa19c156757888c7620459.poster.avif?t=1707744718\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094550/extras/e249eb049dfa19c156757888c7620459.webm?t=1707744718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094550/extras/e249eb049dfa19c156757888c7620459.mp4?t=1707744718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>扮演正义的教士<strong>Cecil</strong>--他可以<strong>进入人们的头脑</strong>，变身为四种独特的恶魔生物，如嚎叫的狼人或凶猛的石像鬼--来对抗七宗罪，解放瘟疫横行的辛维尔村。每种生物都有各自的技能，可以通过敌人掉落的金币进行升级。一旦解锁，你就可以在各种生物之间飞快地切换，每种生物都有一个毁灭性的强力冲刺！[im]{STEAM}。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094550/extras/9b8fce79870bae332357a8fe362c304b.avif?t=1707744718\" width=640 height=100 /></span> 。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094550/extras/4c35050c21fa44033ed40018f9ca563c.poster.avif?t=1707744718\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094550/extras/4c35050c21fa44033ed40018f9ca563c.webm?t=1707744718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094550/extras/4c35050c21fa44033ed40018f9ca563c.mp4?t=1707744718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> 。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在你的恶魔生物之间快速切换，并利用他们独特的能力和射击类型。<br>[列表]<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>嚎叫的狼人</u></strong></h2> 对着月亮嚎叫，产生的声音的频率可以震碎裂开的玻璃，揭示隐藏的秘密。<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>凶猛的夜行神龙</u></strong></h2> 某些物体，如箱子或火炉，可以用夜行神龙的火息点燃，以清理道路，解开秘密或解决谜题。<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Mighty Griffin</u></strong></h2> 只有Mighty Griffin可以爬上布满藤蔓的特殊墙壁，达到新的高度，发现秘密或包抄敌人。<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>最后还有一个秘密的转变...</u></strong></h2> 这最后一个恐怖的生物的力量可能会让你吃惊... 你会有足够的勇气去发现和驯服它吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094550/extras/b2fd0e361950d2ab0b3453e5555e971e.poster.avif?t=1707744718\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094550/extras/b2fd0e361950d2ab0b3453e5555e971e.webm?t=1707744718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094550/extras/b2fd0e361950d2ab0b3453e5555e971e.mp4?t=1707744718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094550/extras/66d4312243922b267549db0b5dfe19af.avif?t=1707744718\" width=640 height=100 /></span> 。<br><br><strong>一个神秘的故事！</strong> 《罪孽传奇》是一个惊心动魄的传奇故事，有令人惊讶的转折，内心的冲突和多种结局。进入所有村民的心灵--无论是罪人还是无辜者--并为等待你的情景和秘密感到惊奇。你是否有足够的力量去发现真相？<br><strong>增强你的技能! </strong> 通过花费敌人掉落的黄金来升级你的恶魔生物。通过掠夺所有隐藏的宝箱和用你的强力冲刺击败敌人，使他们掉落双倍的黄金，从而更快地爬上技能树<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094550/extras/1b52424601cf430af7dd683b285d6727.poster.avif?t=1707744718\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/app